race.comment: BIG PLAYER (2) found some support last start but struggled into fourth (17.00), beaten 5.5 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Looks the one to beat on his best form. SMOOTH BEAUTY (1) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 4.5 lengths third over 400m at this track, clocking 23.44. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Expecting another good run. LET IT LINGER (4) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 400m behind Monkey Magic (23.28) in a Mix 6/7. Placed at her previous run. Some good form is emerging from her last run. One of the main contenders. ELSWYK CINNAMON (7) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - in the mix again.
